name: Matt Braunger: Right Meow (Hour Special Taping)
description: Witness the very first special ever filmed at Bridgetown, just in time for our 10th anniversary, as N.E. Portland native, Matt Braunger, brings all-new material, developed over his last two tours (2016's "Made of Mistakes" and 2017's, "Enraged to be Married") to the Paris Theatre.
